name: Lafanpan | Benriya Saitou-san, Isekai ni Iku
description:
LoRA is generated entirely from anime images.
Should work well with any model.
NSFW works nicely too.

Check samples for prompts :)

1 maderaka = 1 lafanpan = 30cm :D

v1.1

  • for her casual human outfit use tags: brown shirt, beige pants

  • its also much easier to get her to some position

  • for better eyes use tag: blue eyes, detailed eyes

  • i've also managed to replicate her wings use tags: fairy wings, (4 wings:1.6)

basically fixed all the below...

v1.0

Her dress in human form comes out from time to time, it's almost impossible to replicate it everytime :/ I tried almost everything with tags. If you have better luck with it post it! I'm curious!

Her fairy wings are never nicely replicated, the AI just doesn't know they should come from her back and instead it usually places them from her head -_-

So just put it into negatives to gen. her without them. neg. tag: "fairy wings"

Leave a like, comment, review but first of all, ENJOY ;)
